# TOPAS intermediates are NOT tracked. We commit only the post-processed depth
# profiles (results/<plan>/*.dat, written by postprocess_local.py) and the few 2D
# maps (results/<plan>/*.png). Everything below is regenerated by
# run_local.sh + postprocess_local.py and stays local.

# Raw TOPAS run output (scratch): results/output/<plan>/
results/output/

# Native TOPAS scorer artifacts anywhere under data/topas/ (kept local, not committed)
*.csv
*.dcm
